  "lyricsSegments": [
    {
      "end": 27.18000030517578,
      "text": "I'm thinking, I'll make you mine, yeah Hey girl, don't trip, I'm thinking, I'll make",
      "start": 13.800000190734863
    },
    {
      "end": 28.079999923706055,
      "text": "you mine, yeah",
      "start": 27.18000030517578
    },
    {
      "end": 32.619998931884766,
      "text": "Hey girl, don't trip, I'm walking through the night",
      "start": 28.520000457763672
    },
    {
      "end": 38.52000045776367,
      "text": "I see a light above and all above the tunnels in my mind",
      "start": 32.619998931884766
    },
    {
      "end": 42.439998626708984,
      "text": "But I'm thinking, can I clutch you in?",
      "start": 38.52000045776367
    },
    {
      "end": 49.099998474121094,
      "text": "Or was it another false hallucination of me and my dreams, am I just wasting time?",
      "start": 43.13999938964844
    },
    {
      "end": 56.81999969482422,
      "text": "I see that look in your eyes, you're hypnotizing my mind",
      "start": 51.31999969482422
    },
    {
      "end": 71.0199966430664,
      "text": "Hey girl, don't trip, but, that look up in your eyes got my mind drifting",
      "start": 65
    },
    {
      "end": 74.9800033569336,
      "text": "Got me thinking of the ways we can come together, how we can all be hooked",
      "start": 71.08000183105469
    },
    {
      "end": 78.30000305175781,
      "text": "I'm growing, I'm like 24-7 and you know that you're there",
      "start": 74.9800033569336
    },
    {
      "end": 81.23999786376953,
      "text": "Wanna text you all day, wanna know when you're near",
      "start": 78.55999755859375
    },
    {
      "end": 83.66000366210938,
      "text": "You're like my only light, give me a minute my dear",
      "start": 81.23999786376953
    },
    {
      "end": 87.83999633789062,
      "text": "I understand that life goes so much ways and that ways and up downs and that",
      "start": 83.66000366210938
    },
    {
      "end": 91.26000213623047,
      "text": "But I can see the true heart in you, I've seen it through it from the start",
      "start": 87.83999633789062
    },
    {
      "end": 97.58000183105469,
      "text": "No judgement from you, it's kinda new, me and this, new reality and attitude",
      "start": 91.26000213623047
    },
    {
      "end": 103.5199966430664,
      "text": "Hey girl, that look up in your eyes, you got me hypnotized",
      "start": 97.58000183105469
    },
    {
      "end": 108.19999694824219,
      "text": "I'm thinking that I'll make you mine, don't trip",
      "start": 104.0199966430664
    },
    {
      "end": 113.31999969482422,
      "text": "That look up in your eyes, you got me hypnotized",
      "start": 108.19999694824219
    },
    {
      "end": 117.4000015258789,
      "text": "Said, maybe I'll, maybe I'll make you mine, don't trip",
      "start": 113.77999877929688
    },
    {
      "end": 120.31999969482422,
      "text": "Don't think it's more, than the love you get",
